text: Telekabel is a cable television operator and Internet Service Provider for Cable Internet in North Macedonia headquartered in Štip, North Macedonia. They also offer Telephony services. The company relays more than 60 analogue channels, more than 50 digital channels and nine HD channels. ==See also== * Television in Macedonia ==External links== * Telekabel on avmu.mk ==References== Category:Telecommunications in North Macedonia Category:Telecommunications companies established in 1997 Category:North Macedonian companies established in 1997
